Search for-sale properties.

optional_parameters.name: community_ammenities
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more from following options: `community_swimming_pool|community_spa_or_hot_tub|community_golf|community_security_features|community_boat_facilities|tennis_court|community_clubhouse|senior_community`

optional_parameters.name: has_virtual_tours
optional_parameters.description: `true` for properties with virtual tour only. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.description: One of the following options: `relevant|newest|lowest_price|highest_price|open_house_date|price_reduced_date|largest_sqft|lot_size|sold_date`. Default is relevant

optional_parameters.name: lot_views
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more from following options: `waterfront|cul_de_sac|corner_lot|golf_course_lot_or_frontage|hill_or_mountain_view|ocean_view|lake_view|river_view`

optional_parameters.name: has_3d_tours
optional_parameters.description: `true` for properties with 3D tour only. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.name: property_type_nyc_only

optional_parameters.name: inside_rooms
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more comma separated from following options: `basement|hardwood_floors|fireplace|disability_features|den_or_office|family_room|dining_room`

optional_parameters.name: heating_cooling
optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. One or more from following options: `central_air|central_heat|forced_air`

optional_parameters.name: features_in_nyc_only

optional_parameters.name: price_reduced
optional_parameters.description: `true` for properties with price reduced only. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.description: Comma separated values. Get popular keywords from `/keywords-search-suggest` response

optional_parameters.name: expand_search_radius
optional_parameters.description: One of the following options: `1|5|10|25|50`. Expand search by radius in miles

optional_parameters.name: no_hoa_fee
optional_parameters.description: `true` for properties without HOA fee only. Leave blank for any

optional_parameters.name: include_nearby_areas_slug_id
